edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.client

Class GuidEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.client.BasicGuidEntry
      • edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.client.GuidEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GuidEntry
extends edu.umass.cs.gnsclient.client.BasicGuidEntry
implements Serializable
    This class defines a GuidEntry which contains the alias, guid, public and private key. It encapsulates the values the client needs to send and receive queries from the server. Most or all of the client calls use this data structure. This class is Serializable so that it can be read and written to the local file system. IT WILL NEVER BE WRITTEN REMOTELY AS WE DON'T TRANSMIT OR STORE PRIVATE KEYS REMOTELY.
